<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/how-cheney-and-his-allies-created-the-north-korea-nuclear-missile-crisis/">How Cheney and His Allies Created the North Korea Nuclear Missile Crisis</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Cheney set out to sabotage diplomacy.</div>
</div>
